Enum BinaryOperator

      edu.cmu.cs.crystal.tac.BinaryOperator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BinaryOperator>
public enum BinaryOperator
extends java.lang.Enum<BinaryOperator>

Binary operators including arithmetic, relational, and bitwise operators as well as bit shifts and string concatenation. Notice that we distinguish addition (ARIT_ADD) from string concatenation (STRING_CONCAT), even though both are written + (plus) in the source. Also notice that + (plus) and - (minus) can also be BinaryOperators.

Author:
Kevin Bierhoff
